*xfdesktop-4.4.2-r2 (21 Mar 2008)

  21 Mar 2008; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org>
  -files/xfdesktop-4.4.2-memory-leak.patch,
  +files/xfdesktop-4.4.2-relocation-and-memleak.patch,
  -xfdesktop-4.4.2-r1.ebuild, +xfdesktop-4.4.2-r2.ebuild:
  More memory leak fixes from upstream subversion. Extra hunk to fix pic
  relocation bug 211861 from Mandriva, thanks to Walter Meinl.

